---
title: Pork & Red Pesto Spaghetti with Zesty Parmesan Pangrattato
description: Spag bol night just got a whole lot better! Add our vibrant red pesto to give this meal an instant flavour boost, then add a zesty
pangrattato to offset the rich and meaty flavours of the pork bolognese sauce. Bellissimo!
